🔐 AUTH
  POST   /api/v1/auth/register        → Register company + admin user
  POST   /api/v1/auth/login           → Get JWT tokens
  POST   /api/v1/auth/refresh         → Refresh access token
  GET    /api/v1/auth/me              → Get current user

📊 DASHBOARD
  GET    /api/v1/dashboard            → Full dashboard data + charts

📦 PRODUCTS
  GET    /api/v1/products             → List products (paginated, searchable)
  POST   /api/v1/products             → Create product
  GET    /api/v1/products/{id}        → Get single product
  PUT    /api/v1/products/{id}        → Update product
  DELETE /api/v1/products/{id}        → Soft delete product

🏢 WAREHOUSES
  GET    /api/v1/warehouses           → List warehouses + utilization
  POST   /api/v1/warehouses           → Create warehouse
  PUT    /api/v1/warehouses/{id}      → Update warehouse
  DELETE /api/v1/warehouses/{id}      → Soft delete warehouse

📋 INVENTORY
  GET    /api/v1/inventory            → List inventory items
  POST   /api/v1/inventory/stock-in   → Add stock
  POST   /api/v1/inventory/stock-out  → Remove stock
  POST   /api/v1/inventory/transfer   → Transfer between warehouses
  GET    /api/v1/inventory/movements  → Stock movement history

⚠️ ALERTS
  GET    /api/v1/alerts               → List alerts (filterable)
  POST   /api/v1/alerts/mark-read     → Mark specific alerts as read
  POST   /api/v1/alerts/mark-all-read → Mark all alerts as read

📈 REPORTS
  GET    /api/v1/reports/inventory-valuation  → Inventory value report
  GET    /api/v1/reports/stock-movement       → Movement log report
  GET    /api/v1/reports/warehouse-stock      → Per-warehouse stock

🤖 AI (All powered by Groq llama-3.3-70b-versatile)
  POST   /api/v1/ai/product-description → Generate product copy
  GET    /api/v1/ai/inventory-insights  → AI inventory analysis
  POST   /api/v1/ai/chat               → ARIA chat assistant
  POST   /api/v1/ai/demand-forecast     → Demand forecasting
